Package ch.pschatzmann.common.table

Class TablePositive

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.common.table.TablePositive
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITable<java.lang.Number>, java.io.Serializable

    public class TablePositive
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITable<java.lang.Number>
    Returns only absolute positive or negative values (if positive == false). A pie chart does not accept any negative values. The class can be used to present a pie chart of profits (positive values) and a pie chart of losses (with negative values)
    Author:
    pschatzmann
